# .NET 标准 gitignore
# https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore

## 编译产物
bin/
obj/
publish/

## 用户特定文件
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs

## NuGet
packages/
*.nupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/*
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

## VS 缓存
.vs/
*.csproj.user
*.dbmdl
*.jfm

## 运行时生成的文件
replace_rules.json

## 快捷方式
*.lnk

## IDE
.idea/
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
